import { Dialog, DialogContent, DialogTitle, FilledInput, Grid } from '@material-ui/core'
import React from 'react'

const JobModalBox = () => {
    return (
        <Dialog open={true} fullWidth>
            <DialogTitle>Job Post</DialogTitle>
            <DialogContent>
                <Grid container spacing={2}>
                    <Grid item xs={6}>
                        <FilledInput placeholder="Job title" disableUnderline />
                    </Grid>
                </Grid>
            </DialogContent>
        </Dialog>
    )
}

export default JobModalBox
